Class AbstractArraySorter<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorters.AbstractArraySorter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BubbleSorter, HeapSorter, InsertionSorter, PermutationSorter

    public abstract class AbstractArraySorter<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class models a AbstractArraySorter object that will be able to sort arrays according to subclasses implementing sort algorithms.
